Buffett To Retain Washington Post Shares After Leaving Publisher’s Board

-- B y   A n d r e w   F r y e   a n d   M a r g a r e t   C o l l i n s
-- 
2011-04-30T18:33:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-30/buffett-to-retain-washington-post-shares-after-leaving-publisher-s-board.html
Warren Buffett intends to retain
 Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A) ’s stake in  Washington Post Co. (WPO)  after
announcing his plan to step down from the board of the
publishing company.  “I’ll be unequivocal about that,” said Buffett, at
today’s annual Berkshire meeting in Omaha, Nebraska. He said
he’d be available to advise the publishing company’s management
if asked.  To contact the reporter on this story:
